Mon Jul 13 10:00:49 UTC 2026 - Nassim Lhadj <lhadjnassim311@gmail.com>

- Update to version 1.3.0+git21.cbfdd73:
  * Add `gtk_layer_set_respect_close()`/`gtk_layer_get_respect_close()` to the core library API
  * Add support for Layer Shell protocol v5 (includes exclusive edge support)
  * Ignore `.closed` events by default (see gtk3-layer-shell, (fixes #209) )
  * Fix use-after-free when destroying lock windows owned by a GtkApplication (fixes #122)
  * Hold a strong ref to windows while presenting them during session lock (fixes #106)
  * Do not remap unmapped windows on monitor change (fixes #104)
  * Refactor how output slots are handled
  * Improve and refactor the test suite
  * Various other fixes and code cleanups

